1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 20=

21
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,510
Ruizhu.

22
00:01:32,510 --> 00:01:33,370
What brings you here?

23
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:35,590
Concubine De misses the snacks you make.

24
00:01:35,700 --> 00:01:37,200
She begged the Empress Dowager for it.

25
00:01:37,590 --> 00:01:39,310
She wants the recipe for your snacks.

26
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:40,640
The Empress Dowager couldn't refuse.

27
00:01:40,880 --> 00:01:41,840
So she agreed to let you

28
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,640
go to her palace to teach her.

29
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,840
If you really don't want to go,

30
00:01:48,430 --> 00:01:50,430
I can tell the Empress Dowager...

31
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,680
It's fine.

32
00:01:52,710 --> 00:01:53,920
I'll prepare the ingredients

33
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:54,870
and go right away.

34
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,840
(What's meant to come will come.)

35
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,760
(I can't)

36
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,120
(avoid trouble forever.)

37
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,710
(So I'd better face it head-on.)

38
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,750
Concubine De

39
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,360
wants the apple cakes you make.

40
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,400
Finish them within an hour.

41
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:22,710
An hour?

42
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,590
I need at least two maids

43
00:02:28,590 --> 00:02:29,910
for fire and kneading.

44
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:30,990
There are none.

45
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,400
Our Concubine just entered the palace.

46
00:02:34,030 --> 00:02:36,150
Palace affairs
haven't been arranged yet.

47
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,400
No one can be assigned to you.

48
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,680
Aren't you two here?

49
00:02:38,910 --> 00:02:40,400
If you're so free,

50
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,800
stay and start the fire for me.

51
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,030
We're not low-rank maids now.

52
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,430
We're second-class maids

53
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,840
serving Concubine De in her hall.

54
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:48,870
Exactly.

55
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:50,120
Get on with it yourself.

56
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,360
We'll come back

57
00:02:51,360 --> 00:02:52,430
for the cakes in an hour.

58
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,280
Your Ladyship, the snacks are ready.

59
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,360
Too much sugar.

60
00:03:41,590 --> 00:03:42,910
Tell her to make them again.

61
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,030
Yes.

62
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,800
Your Ladyship,
Miss Ye Jin made another batch.

63
00:04:03,910 --> 00:04:04,750
Too bland.

64
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,960
Make it again.

65
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:17,830
Concubine De said

66
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,240
they're tasteless.

67
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,080
Fine.

68
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,800
I'll make another pot.

69
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,920
If it's not right this time,

70
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,360
then I'll make yet another pot.

71
00:04:27,500 --> 00:04:29,190
Concubine De
has all the patience in the world.

72
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,190
Why are you getting worked up?

73
00:04:30,310 --> 00:04:31,470
- You...
- What?

74
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,360
Got nothing to do?

75
00:04:32,390 --> 00:04:33,240
Come, start the fire.

76
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,080
Come here.

77
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,950
In your dreams!

78
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,350
Still here?

79
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:44,510
So foolish.

80
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:07,030
Too greasy.

81
00:05:07,870 --> 00:05:08,710
Take it away.

82
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,070
Too dry.

83
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,120
Too soft.

84
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,230
Too hard.

85
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,240
This color

86
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:33,480
doesn't please me.

87
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:37,840
This pattern

88
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,510
doesn't please me either.

89
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,950
The shape is off.

90
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,510
It's too cold.

91
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,430
I already said that.

92
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,040
Concubine De said

93
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,390
the heat wasn't proper this time.

94
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,190
Please, Miss Ye Jin,

95
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,270
make them once more.

96
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,390
There's no flour left.

97
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,830
We don't care.

98
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,070
We'll come back

99
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,190
for the snacks in an hour anyway.

100
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,750
Even a good cook can't
make food without ingredients

101
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:24,390
So Concubine De
is making things hard for me on purpose.

102
00:06:24,600 --> 00:06:26,310
Even if she is,

103
00:06:26,430 --> 00:06:27,750
what can you do?

104
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,200
Shut up!

105
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:32,960
Chuntao.

106
00:06:33,270 --> 00:06:34,190
Talking nonsense

107
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:35,800
and ruining
Concubine De's reputation.

108
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,720
Chuntao,

109
00:06:38,750 --> 00:06:39,600
Miss Ye Jin,

110
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:41,070
you've had a hard day.

111
00:06:41,510 --> 00:06:43,270
Concubine De feels deeply sorry for it.

112
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,750
Please go back and rest.

113
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,430
These two sisters

114
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,830
served Consort Lan first.

115
00:06:53,190 --> 00:06:56,390
Now they serve Concubine De.

116
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,270
They really know

117
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,680
their way around the palace.

118
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,360
Chuntao,

119
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,750
don't listen to her lies.

120
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:09,240
We're just low maids
from the Consort's palace.

121
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:11,310
Exactly. We had a grudge before.

122
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,750
She's deliberately stirring up trouble.

123
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:28,720
Prince.

124
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,630
You...

125
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:31,070
What happened here?

126
00:07:31,470 --> 00:07:32,360
I...

127
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,310
went

128
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,830
to make some snacks.

129
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:37,040
You've made them many times before.

130
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,750
Why did you

131
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,360
end up like this?

132
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,560
Everyone makes mistakes.

133
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,070
Even the best slip up.

134
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,390
I'm so tired, Your Highness.

135
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,830
I'll go back and rest first.

136
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:02,950
Your Highness.

137
00:08:02,950 --> 00:08:03,950
I've found out everything.

138
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,120
It was Concubine De

139
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,830
who summoned Miss Ye Jin over.

140
00:08:07,190 --> 00:08:09,870
She said she loves
the snacks Miss Ye Jin makes.

141
00:08:10,310 --> 00:08:12,510
So she wanted Miss Ye Jin
to teach her personally.

142
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,270
I see.

143
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,270
You may go.

144
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,320
Yes.

145
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,520
I...

146
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:39,480
If Concubine De summons you again,

147
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:40,600
you don't have to go.

148
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:43,670
I'm just a lowly maid.

149
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,120
How dare I disobey Concubine De?

150
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,510
This is my grudge with her.

151
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:51,200
I'll speak to her myself.

152
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:53,480
Your Highness.

153
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,600
Meeting His Majesty's
concubine in private.

154
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,360
Don't you fear His Majesty
will suspect you more?

155
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,030
My brother's suspicion of me...

156
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,870
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

157
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,440
Rise.

158
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:17,270
How are you doing in her palace?

159
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:18,150
Your Ladyship.

160
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,790
I'm in Concubine De's palace,

161
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:22,200
but my heart is with you.

162
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,670
I know your loyalty.

163
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,480
When this is over,

164
00:09:26,750 --> 00:09:29,200
the position of my first-class maid

165
00:09:29,200 --> 00:09:30,600
will be yours.

166
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:32,160
Thank you, Your Ladyship.

167
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,910
Your Ladyship,

168
00:09:33,910 --> 00:09:36,000
everyone says Concubine De is favored,

169
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:39,480
but His Majesty rarely visits her.

170
00:09:40,120 --> 00:09:41,440
And even when he comes,

171
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,320
they're distant with each other.

172
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,510
Oh?

173
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:48,080
When I attended Concubine De
at her noon rest,

174
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:51,390
I heard her whisper
the 14th Prince's name in her sleep.

175
00:09:56,510 --> 00:09:58,320
I didn't expect that

176
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:02,600
she's such a lovesick soul.

177
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,510
But a romantic

178
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:08,550
has no place in the palace.

179
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:26,270
Concubine De
has been in the palace for days.

180
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:29,670
I hear His Majesty is cold to her.

181
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:31,120
Mother, you know full well.

182
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:33,030
She never cared for me from the start.

183
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,240
Her heart is with the 14th Prince.

184
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,150
Why should I fawn over someone

185
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:38,790
who doesn't love me?

186
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,000
I understand.

187
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,840
I don't favor her.

188
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,510
She's the daughter

189
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:47,080
of the General of Martial Might,
sent here personally.

190
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,150
But you must know,

191
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:51,840
the Lan clan is too powerful in court.

192
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,720
Lan Shiheng commands
a huge army at the border.

193
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:58,120
Consort Lan dominates the harem.

194
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,120
It breeds instability.

195
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:03,000
I'm just using her to balance the power.

196
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,550
I understand.

197
00:11:05,150 --> 00:11:06,150
But courtesy is one thing,

198
00:11:06,150 --> 00:11:07,080
and feelings are another.

199
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,150
Since she doesn't care,

200
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:09,390
I won't force her.

201
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,910
I'll keep her dignity intact,

202
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,510
so no one mocks her.

203
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:17,790
Now every time
His Majesty comes to the harem,

204
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:20,150
he almost always comes by my place.

205
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:22,320
Even if he doesn't stay the night,

206
00:11:22,670 --> 00:11:24,670
he still eats and talks with me.

207
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:27,720
But in my heart,

208
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,630
I always feel uneasy.

209
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:34,120
His Majesty truly cares for you.

210
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:38,720
An Emperor's heart
is the hardest to read.

211
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:41,600
Consort Lan
made such a terrible mistake,

212
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:43,670
yet His Majesty only confined her.

213
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,790
If she regains favor,

214
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:48,320
she'll come for me first.

215
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,030
And Concubine De.

216
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,360
She became a Concubine
as soon as she entered.

217
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,390
The look in her eyes

218
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,600
shows she's not easy to deal with.

219
00:11:57,150 --> 00:11:57,990
If I...

220
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,870
Why are you looking at me like that?

221
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:08,030
The Hui I remember
was always calm and steady.

222
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:09,750
You knew your place.

223
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,390
I've rarely seen you

224
00:12:11,390 --> 00:12:13,360
so anxious and suspicious.

225
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:17,200
I've been too impatient lately.

226
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:18,870
I just

227
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:20,910
want to clear my father's name soon.

228
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,960
There's no need to rush.

229
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:26,080
His Majesty
already dislikes Consort Lan.

230
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,670
He just fears her father and brother.

231
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,790
As for Concubine De,

232
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:32,270
she doesn't love His Majesty.

233
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:34,000
Even if she holds a high rank,

234
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,030
His Majesty won't care about her.

235
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:43,510
So those rumors are true.

236
00:12:43,670 --> 00:12:44,600
What rumors?

237
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,360
I just heard some maids

238
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,960
gossiping in the Imperial Garden.

239
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,600
They said Concubine De
still loves the 14th Prince.

240
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,360
She entered the palace to
be closer to him.

241
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,910
Now she thinks of him
every day in the palace

242
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:57,390
and refuses to share His Majesty's bed.

243
00:12:57,720 --> 00:13:00,270
Whoever spread this is vicious.

244
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:03,360
It's meant to destroy Concubine De
and the 14th Prince.

245
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,240
Exactly.

246
00:13:04,480 --> 00:13:06,750
If His Majesty hears this,

247
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:08,390
not only will Concubine De suffer,

248
00:13:08,670 --> 00:13:10,600
the 14th Prince will be implicated too.

249
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:13,960
You must warn
the 14th Prince to prepare.

250
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,120
Not for now.

251
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:17,600
The key isn't the 14th Prince.

252
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,550
It's Concubine De.

253
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,320
Concubine De is no pushover.

254
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:22,150
She's much smarter than Consort Duan.

255
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,080
She'll know how to handle this.

256
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:29,390
Your Majesty,
please uphold justice for me.

257
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,360
Child,

258
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,390
rise and speak.

259
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:34,510
I was once betrothed to the 14th Prince,

260
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,910
but that's in the past.

261
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:38,240
You know that, Your Majesty.

262
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:40,390
There's nothing between us.

263
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,550
Now that I'm in the palace,

264
00:13:42,550 --> 00:13:43,750
I belong to His Majesty,

265
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,480
so I should serve
His Majesty wholeheartedly.

266
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:48,750
But I don't know who I offended.

267
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,750
Vicious rumors
have been spread about me.

268
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,910
They say I still love the 14th Prince.

269
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:56,480
If this spreads,

270
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:58,750
it will drive me to my death.

271
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:07,960
Your Majesty.

272
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,840
You're a smart girl.

273
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,600
Now that this has happened,

274
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:14,510
I must say something.

275
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,200
You're partly to blame for

276
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:20,150
these rumors spreading.

277
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:22,360
Your Majesty, I...

278
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,720
Don't rush to explain yourself.

279
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,120
I didn't say you did anything,

280
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:28,320
but I know exactly

281
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,390
what's in your heart.

282
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,670
Since you're in the palace,

283
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,080
you're a royal consort.

284
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:36,480
You must let go of your old feelings.

285
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,510
The harem is no place
to hide from the world.

286
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,150
If you want to live well here,

287
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:42,670
you must stand on your own.

288
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,720
If you cannot stand on your own,

289
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,600
no one can help you.

290
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,200
Not even me.

291
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:53,960
Enough.

292
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:54,910
As for these rumors,

293
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:56,510
I'll investigate

294
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,750
and deal with them.

295
00:14:57,750 --> 00:15:01,240
But you must learn from this.

296
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,600
Go back and think carefully.

297
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:07,120
How to protect yourself

298
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,000
and your family's honor?

299
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:10,840
Yes.

300
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,790
I understand.

301
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:20,000
♪I am but an outsider♪

302
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:22,200
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

303
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:26,480
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

304
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:30,720
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

305
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:38,240
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

306
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:41,800
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

307
00:15:41,800 --> 00:15:44,320
♪I know how this story ends♪

308
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:48,880
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

309
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:53,320
♪Truth or lie—I can't tell♪

310
00:15:58,280 --> 00:16:01,600
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

311
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:04,880
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

312
00:16:05,080 --> 00:16:08,160
♪A history that no one can search♪

313
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:11,680
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

314
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,480
♪I am but an outsider♪

315
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:15,720
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

316
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:19,760
♪Outwit the world
but not the way we meet♪

317
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:24,440
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

318
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:31,760
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

319
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:35,120
♪In a world of lies,
you're all that's clear♪

320
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:37,600
♪I know how this story ends♪

321
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:41,760
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

322
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:45,040
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

323
00:16:45,040 --> 00:16:48,840
♪Please forget me and move on♪

324
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:55,080
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

325
00:16:58,240 --> 00:17:06,600
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

326
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:19,880
♪When do I finally wake♪
